Currency Converter Application
run:

    pip install flask requests
    python currency_converter_app.py

Open http://127.0.0.1:5000 in your browser.

Features:
- Simple, clean UI (Bootstrap CDN)
- Live exchange rates from exchangerate.host (free, no API key required)
- Fallback static rates if the online API fails
- Input validation and helpful error messages
- Example supported currencies list

Note: This is for local use only. Don't expose to the public without proper security.
